**Examples of Commercial Use (Prohibited):**
- Offering this Software as a SaaS (Software-as-a-Service)
- Selling compiled versions or distributions
- Charging for hosting/installation services
- Including in a commercial music management suite
- Using to provide paid playlist synchronization services
- Incorporating into a commercial Navidrome hosting service

**Examples of Non-Commercial Use (Allowed):**
- Personal use on your home server
- Educational use in schools/universities
- Community-hosted instances without profit
- Hosting for friends/family at no cost
- Open-source contributions and forks
- Academic research and teaching

